comments:
Renamed 24.11.1988 to become the parish of Aston, Cote, 
    Shifford & Chimney. See also Table 2, note (b).

Created 24.11.1988 by renaming the parish of Aston Bampton & 
    Shifford. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1.4.1985 out of the parish of Carterton & Black 
    Bourton. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 1.4.1985 out of the parishes of Brize Norton and 
    Carterton. See also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 1.4.1985 and divided between the parishes of 
    Alvescot, Black Bourton, Carterton and Clanfield. See also Table 2, note 
    (b).

Abolished 1.4.1985 and added to the parish of Woodstock. See 
    also Table 2, note (a).
